WHAT IS UP WITH OUR DATES AND WHY DO THEY KEEP GETTING BETTER?!?!! 

Ngl. I expected this date to end with just us having fun talking with each other, enjoying each other's company, hugging, and yes, lots of pecks on the lips (and cheeks, and nose, and forehead). 

Pero yon?!?!? 

That was kissing with the capital K. I. Double S. I. N. G. 

Jusq. I could feel my self heat up just from remembering!!!! 

I enjoyed it a lot, Rei! Thank you so much!!!! You make me the happiest. I'm really grateful that you reciprocate my feelings for me. I love you so much!! 

Jusq Raph kalma.  HAHAHAHAHAH. Namumula nanaman ako.
